"如果您希望强制使用强密码，参考 <ulink url=\"&blfs-book;postlfs/cracklib."
"html\"/> 以在构建 Shadow 前安装 CrackLib。然后，将 <parameter>--with-"
"libcrack</parameter> 添加到下面的 <command>configure</command> 命令中。"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:52
msgid ""
"Disable the installation of the <command>groups</command> program and its "
"man pages, as Coreutils provides a better version. Also, prevent the "
"installation of manual pages that were already installed in <xref "
"linkend=\"ch-system-man-pages\"/>:"
msgstr ""
"禁止该软件包安装 <command>groups</command> 程序和它的 man 页面，因为 "
"Coreutils 会提供更好的版本。同样，避免安装<xref linkend=\"ch-system-man-"
"pages\"/>软件包已经提供的 man 页面："

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:57
#, no-wrap
